										This wonderful website has kindly been created with much love and skill by an alumna of our Tibetan Course and dear friend, Laurane Boulenger ལགས།. She also creates and designs amazing <a href="https://www.francaisavecpierreetnoel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-600 hover:underline">French Courses</a> and <a href="https://padlet.com/lauraneboulenger/useful-resources-links-to-tibetan-and-study-materials-edjl7v68j9h9tykn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-600 hover:underline">Tibetan language study materials</a>. But, what she loves the most are རི་བོང་། (bunnies).
