										Designing and offering all these innovative and engaging Tibetan language Courses and resources became possible thanks to the incredible and skilful support of Tsering Gellek ལགས།. She is the director of <a href="https://sini.education/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-600 hover:underline">SINI</a>, the Sarnath International Nyingma Institute. SINI's motto is "Building Bridges of Goodness". Countless such bridges have been and continue to be built by our dedicated students and committed colleagues at SINI all over the world. Tsering Gellek ལགས།'s skilful leadership, complete trust and deep love for our project is a guiding light for which I'm deeply grateful.
									</p>
