										SINI would not exist if it wasn't for Tsering Gellek ལགས།'s father, <a href="https://nyingmainstitute.com/about-us/tarthang-tulku-rinpoche/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-600 hover:underline">Tarthang Tulku Rinpoche</a> asking her to build such an Institute. Upon hearing about Tarthang Tulku Rinpoche's life-long, tireless commitment to the preservation of the Dharma, meeting Tsering Gellek ལགས། and some of his dedicated disciples in 2018, I decided to leave my job at UVa and join SINI instead. Tarthang Tulku Rinpoche with his incredible visionary mind and unceasing Dharma activities at the age of 90 is a true source of inspiration and I'm deeply humbled.
